'''Trebor''' was a name shared by a number of individuals:
*[[Trebor]], a [[Human/Legends|Human]] who served as copilot aboard the cargo [[Shuttle/Legends|shuttle]] ''[[Moon Dash]]''.
*[[Coleman Trebor/Legends|Coleman Trebor]], a [[Vurk/Legends|Vurk]] [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] who was killed in the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|Battle of Geonosis]]
*[[Epoh Trebor]], a [[Human/Legends|Human]] comedian.

